Interface JpaCriteriaBuilder

All Superinterfaces:
CriteriaBuilder
All Known Implementing Classes:

public interface JpaCriteriaBuilder extends CriteriaBuilder
PUBLIC: EclipseLInk specific JPA Criteria interface. Provides the functionality defined in jakarta.persistence.criteria.CriteriaBuilder and adds EclipseLink specific functionality.
